pos_examples: Now, pop start pipe teddy from area bastion to area rain with batch-atom kumquat, batch-atom dress_red, product kumquat_8, and product socket.
(pop-start teddy kumquat bastion rain dress_red kumquat_8 socket)
Once you are done, please pop end pipe object_260 from area object_50 to area screen with batch-atom yew and batch-atom roof_11.

First, pop unitary pipe frame_9 with batch-atom dress_red from area screen to area object_50 replacing batch-atom yew using product fire and product socket and then push end pipe star_213 from area screen to area object_50 with batch-atom yew and batch-atom yew_35.

(pop-unitarypipe frame_9 dress_red object_50 screen yew fire socket)
(push-end star_213 screen object_50 yew yew_35)
The next step is to push unitary pipe teddy with batch-atom yew_35 from area rain to area screen replacing batch-atom kumquat using product kumquat_8 and product kumquat_8_63.
(push-unitarypipe teddy yew_35 rain screen kumquat kumquat_8 kumquat_8_63)
